blueprint.label: Double-Rail (small city block, not recommended)
blueprint.description:
If you want city blocks like this, it's better to use the rail templates from the self-building factory:
https://factorioprints.com/view/-MNZWdWosuqr3vtaC2hD

Those have been optimized to make better use of the straight sections, something that isn't possible when just putting straight/corner pieces together in an arbitrary configuration.
